subject: Golf
PGA Championship
lead_paragraph: The 27-year-old Australian remained in position for a wire-to-wire victory as he fired a two-under-par 69 to reach 20-under 193 in the third of four tournaments in the PGA Tour’s FedEx Cup playoffs.
